description: Outline application for demolition of some existing buildings and Creation of up to 1,296 residential dwellings; Creation of up to 77 one-bedroom assisted living retirement accommodation; Creation of a three-form entry primary school; Creation of a hotel (Class C1) of up to 90 beds; Creation of a 1,200 seat theatre with ancillary cafe (Sui Generis); office (Class B1a) of up to 13,860sq.m; energy centre (Sui Generis) of up to 1,200sq.m; and retail (Class A1, A2, A3, A4, A5) of up to 2,850sq m; Creation of a local centre to provide up to 150sq.m of retail (Class A1 and A2) and 225sq.m GP surgery (Class D1); Means of access and improvements to pedestrian linkages to the Uxbridge Town centre; car parking; provision of public open space including a district park; landscaping; sustainable infrastructure and servicing 2. In addition to the above, full planning permission for 28 residential dwellings; Change of use to provide 16 dwellings
